Paladin/Fighter:
1 - 7 = PREV_EXP * 2
8     = PREV_EXP * 2 - 3000
9-20  = PREV_EXP + 250000

Ranger:
1 - 6  = PREV_EXP * 2
7      = PREV_EXP * 2 + 3000
8 - 20 = PREV_EXP + 300000


